    "For example, knowledge databases in the clinical toolbox enhance the medical knowledge of the agent, and calculators give the agent the ability to calculate indicators accurately.",
    "In order to allow the agent to solve problems more flexibly, we did not limit the types and number of tools when solving a specific type of task.",
